These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  photographer, librarian, manager, social-worker, dancer, software-developer, musician
1. the librarian is in the middle##1
2. the librarian is on the left of the manager##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the social-worker##1
4. the photographer is on the right of the manager##1
5. the musician is on the far left##1
6. the software-developer is on the right of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Job   | musician | social-worker | dancer | librarian | manager | photographer | software-developer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, february, march, september, april, october, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Birthday   | may | april | march | october | september | february | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, goat, horse, ferret, chinchilla, hamster
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Pet   | ferret | guinea-pig | chinchilla | goat | hamster | rabbit | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
7 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, backgammon, snooker, go, canasta, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7    |
| Game   | chess | snooker | monopoly | mah-jongg | backgammon | go | canasta |

