.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, february, january, september, august, march, june
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Birthday   | june | january | september | march | may | february | august |

