.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, house, trance, electronic, pop, rock, r&b
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of house is on the far right##1
5. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the fan of rock is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |    3    |     4     |       5       |   6   |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | trance | r&b | pop | rock | electronic | disco | house |

