2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3   |   4    |   5   |   6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | skydiving | hiking | fishing | gardening | rock-climbing | chess |

