.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: skateboard, bus, ship, snowmobile, subway, car, helicopter
1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |    4    |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Transport   | snowmobile | helicopter | car | skateboard | subway | ship | bus |

 